---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
	<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
		<img src="https://cdn.freebiesupply.com/logos/large/2x/nodejs-1-logo-png-transparent.png" alt="Nodejs Logo" width="60" height="60" />
		<img src="https://images.icon-icons.com/2699/PNG/512/python_logo_icon_168886.png" alt="Python-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
		<img src="https://www.pngall.com/wp-content/uploads/15/React-Logo-PNG-Images.png" alt="React-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
		<img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*Klh1l7wkoG6PDPb9A5oCHQ.png" alt="Angular-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
		<img src="https://cdn.freebiesupply.com/logos/large/2x/vue-9-logo-png-transparent.png" alt="Vue-Logo" height="48" width="48" />

		</div>
		<h2>Informatics Engineer | Senior Full-Stack Developer</h2>
		<div class="expertise-content">
			<p class="lead">Building Enterprise-Grade Solutions with Modern Web Architectures:</p>
			<ul class="tech-highlights">
				<li>
					<strong>React</strong> - Building dynamic and scalable user interfaces for high-traffic applications.
					<span class="tech-tag">Modern Front-End</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Node.js / Python</strong> - Developing robust and efficient back-end services and APIs for enterprise needs.
					<span class="tech-tag">Scalable Back-End</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Cloud Technologies (AWS/Azure/GCP)</strong> - Architecting and deploying cloud-native solutions for scalability and reliability.
					<span class="tech-tag">Cloud Native</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>AI Integration</strong> - Implementing AI-powered features, including NLP, to enhance application capabilities and user experience.
					<span class="tech-tag">Intelligent Solutions</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Modern Web Architectures</strong> - Designing and implementing microservices and other modern architectural patterns for resilient and maintainable systems.
					<span class="tech-tag">Scalability & Maintainability</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="metrics">
				<div class="metric">
					<span class="number">10+</span>
					<span class="label">Years Experience</span>
				</div>
				<div class="metric">
					<span class="number">40K+</span>
					<span class="label">Daily Users</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
			<img src="https://mediaresource.sfo2.digitaloceanspaces.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/08191327/ChatGPT-Logo-PNG-Green-Color-Design-1.png" alt="ChatGpt Logo" width="60" height="60" />
			<img src="https://static-00.iconduck.com/assets.00/google-cloud-icon-2048x1646-7admxejz.png" alt="Google-Cloud-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
			<img src="https://swimburger.net/media/ppnn3pcl/azure.png" alt="Azure-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
			<img src="https://cdn.iconscout.com/icon/free/png-256/free-aws-logo-icon-download-in-svg-png-gif-file-formats--cloud-computing-network-server-database-brand-pack-logos-icons-1583149.png?f=webp&w=256" alt="Aws-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
		</div>
		<h2>AI Integration Specialist</h2>
		<ul class="tech-highlights">
			<li>Developed NLP-powered solutions for document processing, achieving significant efficiency gains (e.g., 70% reduction in processing time).</li>
			<li>Integrated with AI platforms and APIs (e.g., OpenAI, Google Cloud AI, AWS AI, Azure AI) to enhance application functionality.</li>
			<li>Designed and implemented machine learning models for specific business use cases.</li>
			<li>Leveraged language fluency to tailor AI solutions for multilingual applications and global audiences.</li>
		</ul>
		<div class="metrics">
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">3+</span>
				<span class="label">AI Projects</span>
			</div>
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">NLP</span>
				<span class="label">Expertise</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: center;">
			<img src="https://static-00.iconduck.com/assets.00/google-cloud-icon-2048x1646-7admxejz.png" alt="Google-Cloud-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
			<img src="https://swimburger.net/media/ppnn3pcl/azure.png" alt="Azure-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
			<img src="https://cdn.iconscout.com/icon/free/png-256/free-aws-logo-icon-download-in-svg-png-gif-file-formats--cloud-computing-network-server-database-brand-pack-logos-icons-1583149.png?f=webp&w=256" alt="Aws-Logo" height="48" width="48" />
			<img src="https://cdn4.iconfinder.com/data/icons/logos-and-brands/512/97_Docker_logo_logos-512.png" alt="Docker-Logo" height="48" width="48" />

		</div>
		<h2>Cloud Computing Expertise</h2>
		<ul class="tech-highlights">
			<li>Designed, deployed, and managed scalable and highly available applications on leading cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP).</li>
			<li>Implemented serverless architectures using services like AWS Lambda, Azure Functions, and Google Cloud Functions for cost-effective and event-driven solutions.</li>
			<li>Utilized containerization technologies like Docker and orchestration platforms like Kubernetes for efficient application deployment and management in the cloud.</li>
			<li>Experienced with infrastructure as code (IaC) using tools like Terraform or CloudFormation for automated and repeatable infrastructure provisioning.</li>
		</ul>
		<div class="metrics">
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">3+</span>
				<span class="label">Cloud Platforms</span>
			</div>
			<div class="metric">
				<span class="number">$</span>
				<span class="label">Cost-Efficient</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>



<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.metrics {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: flex-start; /* align left */
		align-items: center;
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap; /* ensures responsiveness on smaller screens */
	}

	.metric {
		background: var(--gray-900);
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
		text-align: center;
		min-width: 120px;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
		flex: 0 0 auto; /* prevent stretching */
	}

	.metric:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
	}

	.metric .number {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--accent-regular, #6366f1);
	}

	.metric .label {
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--gray-400);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
	}


	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>